{"type": "article", "id": 28990, "title": "简洁的桌椅系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-01T06:49:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702171854jedYga58xTsifBFW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.vuue.com.au/\">VUUE</a> 是一个由美国设计师 Ceci Keyvanloo 与澳大利亚设计师和工程师 Aydin Keyvanloo 共同创立的墨尔本家具品牌，他们推出的第一个家具系列名为 Mornington。这些外观简洁现代的桌椅无论是放在室内还是室外都很合适，VUUE 根据放置的位置为顾客提供了不同的定制选择，包括颜色、大小以及材质（希望你没有选择障碍）。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171852Am8lr51QHcWkhs7C.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.58333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171852TwevzDKWaPr9tnU7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171853ksu0YPx5lZ6zdb8K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171853Yl3KC4ZRbm2Fqkcy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}